Package: packagelinreg
Type: Package
Title: Implementation of Linear Regression and QR Decomposition for a University Assignment
Version: 1.0
Date: 2024-10-05
Author: Christian Kammerer, Victor Guillo
Maintainer: Christian Kammerer <chrka821@student.liu.se>
Description: This package implements two key functionalities:
  1. Linear regression using ordinary least squares (OLS) with added support for QR decomposition.
  2. QR decomposition is used to enhance numerical stability when solving linear regression equations.
